agreed to a settlement yesterday.

227
00:11:01,869 --> 00:11:02,744
He must have
misunderstood.

228
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:04,829
We had discussed,
but I never agreed to anything.

229
00:11:04,955 --> 00:11:06,122
Do you have
a signed agreement?

230
00:11:08,125 --> 00:11:09,709
Uh, I...

231
