She made a joke.

238
00:11:23,974 --> 00:11:26,893
The type of joke that
I'm sure every person in this courtroom

239
00:11:27,019 --> 00:11:28,937
has made at
one point or another.

240
00:11:29,063 --> 00:11:30,897
And yet,
she was fired.

241
